 SFDX: Run Apex Tests.
Set Breakpoints and Checkpoints
you can Enter sfdx checkpoint in the search box, then choose SFDX: Toggle Checkpoint.

=======
SFDX: Turn On Apex Debug Log for Replay Debugger.
enter apex test in the search box, then choose SFDX: Run Apex Tests.
enter sfdx get in the search box, then choose SFDX: Get Apex Debug Logs.... After a few seconds, you are prompted to select a debug log to download.


Run apex test  => get log  =>   right click=> launch apex replay  debugger for currenct file
